{"tid":1701322,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"故意惹民憤>不反>腰斬>大圍捕 無限loop","createTime":"2019-11-09T03:55:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T05:16:52.000Z","uid":154702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1fda48784cba0550feb1c2b9f2073ad5745ae25d","tid":1701322,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T03:55:42.000Z","msg":"基本上每個週末都係咁玩<br />\n每到星期二三就有事<br />\n發酵兩日<br />\n週末就出不反預約拘捕<br />\n港共政府志在消磨仲肯出黎既人<br />\n<br />\n<strong>唔好誤會，我唔係叫人唔好出嚟，唔係中計黨</strong><br />\n我意思係當政府有心預約拘捕嘅時候<br />\n我哋更加應該拒絕公式化，思考對策<br />\n細心分析對方棋局<br />\n和理非要有心理準備做<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">被捕師</span></strong><br />\n同時各區開花拉怪都好重要"},{"pid":"6cf454b426c3b2df4b59a2ad713ff109d0057a40","tid":1701322,"uid":154702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"633c100bdba2cc0fd1de839e6934da4c75ba28d2","tid":1701322,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T05:16:52.000Z","msg":"push"}]}